about:
I am an outdoorsy gardener with a big old Portland house.  I am a Mom and my house is just awesome for spending family time.  We love eating at Lovely 50-50, it is the best pizza and house wine. Not your ordinary pizza, the salads are to die for.  We move around quite a bit so our house is available for you to experience. Come on over stay a week or a month or more.  Our family motto:  Respect people and animals;
Do well in school; 
Appreciate the things you have; 
Play fair.
